p%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20the%20back%20room%20of%20a%20Moscow%20restaurant%2C%20the%20lunchtime%20meeting%20involved%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20bites%20of%20food%20interspersed%20with%20large%20shots%20of%20vodka%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20biography.%20The%20Russians%20also%20gifted%20the%20trio%20a%20bottle%20of%20vodka%20each%2C%20where%20the%20label%20was%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20recipient%20on%20Mars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20calculated%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20food%20and%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20vodka%2C%20and%20they%20were%20roughly%20equal%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20in%20the%20biographer's%20words%3A%20%26quot%3BMusk%2C%20who%20was%20holding%20his%20head%20up%20with%20his%20hand%2C%20passed%20out%2C%20and%20his%20head%20slammed%20into%20the%20table.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-dislikes-most-alcohol-but-partial-whiskey-red-wine-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%20said%20he%20dislikes%20%26quot%3Bthe%20taste%20or%20effects%20of%20most%20alcohol%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20expressed%20a%20preference%20for%20red%20wine.%20The%20billionaire%20was%20also%20pictured%20drinking%20from%20a%20wine%20glass%20while%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20Final%20in%20Qatar%20last%20year.%20And%20in%202017%2C%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F872260000491593728%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etweeted%3A%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BA%20little%20red%20wine%2C%20vintage%20record%2C%20some%20Ambien...%20and%20magic!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20passing%20out%20in%20Moscow%2C%20there%20was%20another%20unsuccessful%20meeting%20on%20that%20trip%20before%20Musk%20returned%20in%20early%202002.%20Isaacson%20writes%20that%20he%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20two%20Dnepr%20rockets%20for%20%2418%20million%2C%20but%20the%20Russians%20actually%20wanted%