ssion%20Take%20Up%3F%20No%20One%20Knows%2C%20Not%20Even%20the%20Cabinet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30123153%2Fimage3-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20was%20published%20on%20Saturday%2C%20September%209%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjoint-sitting-of-both-houses-to-bid-farewell-to-old-parliament-building%2Farticleshow%2F103519895.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eheadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CJoint%20sitting%20of%20both%20Houses%20to%20bid%20farewell%20to%20old%20Parliament%20building%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20question%20mark%20is%20normal%2C%20because%20few%20know%20what%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20special%20session%20is.%20The%20report%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CJust%20ahead%20of%20the%20five-day%20special%20session%2C%20there%20is%20considerable%20speculation%20over%20whether%20a%20joint%20meeting%20of%20the%20two%20Houses%20will%20be%20convened%20on%20September%2019%20in%20the%20iconic%20Central%20Hall%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20the%20existing%20Parliament%20building.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20one%20need%20five%20days%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20a%20building%3F%20And%20why%20is%20there%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cconsiderable%20speculation%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20democracy%20when%20laws%20and%20changes%20should%20be%20discussed%20openly%20and%20transparently%3F%20On%20this%2C%20the%20report%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20enlightenment%20to%20readers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20special%20session%20was%20first%20announced%20on%20August%2031%2C%20there%20began%20a%20guessing%20game%20on%20why%20it%20was%20being%20called%20so%20shortly%20after%20one%20session%20had%20just%20ended%20on%20August%2011.%20The%20Winter%20Session%20will%20begin%20in%20November%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20there%20is%20no%20other%20time%20for%20Parliament%20to%20meet.%20Why%20again%20this%20month%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20said%20it%20was%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20the%20country%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbharat-india-hindustan-history%5C%22%3EIndia%20to%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20days%20of%20media%20focus%20went%20into%20that.%20Ministers%20defended%20the%20move%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20it%2C%20but%20were%20unable%20to%20confirm%20whether%20or%20not%20this%20change%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20what%20the%20session%20was%20for.%20Another%20guess%20was%20that%20it%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill.%20This%20was%20originally%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202008%2C%20but%20since%20then%20it%20has%20stalled%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20support%20and%20demands%20of%20sub-reservations%20within%20this%20category%20for%20marginalised%20sections.%20If%20this%20is%20on%20the%20agenda%20and%20it%20goes%20through%2C%20it%20will%20set%20aside%20one-third%20of%20all%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%20for%20women.%20This%20is%20a%20considerable%20reform%2C%20and%20if%20it%20is%20indeed%20this%20law%20that%20is%20being%20taken%20up%2C%20one%20hopes%20that%20it%20passes.%20But%20of%20course%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20guess%20in%20the%20media%20was%20that%20the%20government%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20was%20calling%20the%20general%20election%20early.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20due%20in%20April-May%20next%20year%2C%20meaning%20in%20another%20seven%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20but%20they%20might%20be%20advanced%20just%20as%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20had%20done%20in%202004.%20This%20theory%20has%20not%20found%20many%20takers%2C%20but%20again%2C%20who%20knows%3F%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20gambit%20to%20call%20elections%20early%20did%20not%20succeed%20and%20the%20government%20fell%2C%20so%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20caution%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20fervent%20speculation%20was%20around%20something%20called%20%E2%80%9Cone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20system%20whereby%20all%20states%20and%20the%20Centre%20will%20go%20into%20elections%20every%20five%20years%20together%20and%20citizens%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20Will%20corporation%20elections%20also%20be%20included%3F%20One%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20byelections%3F%20And%20how%20will%20the%20EVMs%20be%20set%20up%20for%20multiple%20elections%3F%20One%20does%20not%20know%20that%20either%2C%20but%20perhaps%20wiser%20minds%20have%20already%20sorted%20all%20such%20things%20out.%20A%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20under%20a%20former%20President%20to%20look%20into%20the%20idea%2C%20but%20how%20this%20committee%20will%20meet%20and%20give%20its%20findings%20all%20in%20time%20for%20the%20special%20session%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20more%20story%20floated%20in%20the%20media%20was%20that%20the%20session%20was%20about%20a%20commission%20set%20up%20in%202017%20to%20look%20at%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBCs%20so%20that%20reservations%20could%20be%20made%20more%20equitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20form%20of%20government%20carries%20with%20it%20something%20called%20collective%20responsibility%2C%20meaning%20that%20decisions%20are%20jointly%20owned.%20But%20here%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20is%20as%20much%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20decisions%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20are.%20Two%20instances%20from%20the%20past%20will%20suffice%20to%20demonstrate%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20a%20report%20from%20November%2010%2C%202016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdon-t-bring-your-phones-modi-s-cabinet-meet-that-took-everyone-by-surprise%2Fstory-YEbaMM3lr3McikFnnSZTmL.html%5C%22%3Eheadlined%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20bring%20your%20phones%3A%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Cabinet%20meet%20that%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise.%E2%80%9D%20The%20report%20said%20Union%20ministers%20found%20out%20about%20demonetisation%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%20meaning%20that%20it%20was%20neither%20discussed%20nor%20debated.%20Another%20instance%20is%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20filing%20of%20over%20240%20Right%20to%20Information%20queries%20with%20the%20government%20about%20the%20national%20lockdown%20of%202020.%20It%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20departments%20of%20health%2C%20finance%2C%20disaster%20management%20and%20the%20rest%20about%20what%20they%20knew%20regarding%20the%20lockdown%20and%20how%20they%20prepared.%20The%20answer%20was%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20and%20did%20not%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20form%20of%20government%2C%20where%20secrets%20and%20major%20decisions%20are%20kept%20from%20the%20Cabinet%20itself%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20continuing%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20speculation%20around%20this%20special%20session.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20Question%20Hour%20either%20in%20this%20session%2C%20and%20while%20this%20is%20expected%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary.%20Even%20questions%20asked%20are%20not%20answered%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20so%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20stopping%20them%20from%20being%20asked%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20sent%20a%20list%20of%20things%20they%20would%20like%20discussed%20in%20the%20session.%20These%20include%20inflation%2C%20joblessness%2C%20MSP%20for%20farmers%2C%20the%20continuing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Adani%20scandal%2C%20communal%20tensions%20across%20India%2C%20the%20Chinese%20actions%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20(or%20any%20census%2C%20given%20that%20the%20primary%20one%20has%20been%20inexplicably%20delayed)%2C%20the%20strains%20on%20federalism%20and%20impact%20of%20natural%20disasters%20and%20climate%20change.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%2C%20assuming%20these%20are%20not%20already%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20they%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20even%20the%20Cabinet%20itself%20has%20such%20little%20say%20in%20what%20should%20be%20discussed%20and%20passed%2C%20why%20should%20the%20Opposition%20be%20listened%20to%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asianage.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumnists%2F120923%2Faakar-patel-what-will-special-session-take-up-no-one-knows-not-even-the-cabinet.html%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Asian%20Age.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-issues-will-the-5-day-special-session-take-up-no-one-knows-not-even-the-cabinet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Winter%20Session%20will%20begin%20in%20November%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20there%20is%20no%20other%20time%20for%20Parliament%20to%20meet.%20Why%20again%20this%20month%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-issues-will-the-5-day-special-session-take-up-no-one-knows-not-even-the-cabinet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20CEO%20lessons%20Elon%20Musk%20tried%20to%20teach%20his%20bother%20Kimbal%2C%20based%20on%20a%20mobile%20game%20Musk%20was%20obsessed%20with%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20picture%20of%20Elon%20and%20Kimbal%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650009af112d1600192d685e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20(left)%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Kimbal%20Musk%20(right).%3Cp%3EJoel%20Saget%2FAFP%20and%20Chris%20Saucedo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202021%2C%20Musk%20became%20obsessed%20with%20the%20mobile%20strategy%20game%20%26quot%3BThe%20Battle%20of%20Polytopia%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20his%20biographer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMusk's%20obsession%20with%20the%20game%20was%20such%20that%20it%20once%20delayed%20a%20meeting%20with%20managers%20and%20even%20caused%20a%20big%20fight%20with%20Grimes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMusk%20also%20handed%20down%20eight%20CEO%20lessons%20to%20his%20brother%20Kimbal%20through%20the%20game.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20cited%20a%20host%20of%20video%20game%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-draws-inspiration-sci-fi-selectively-spacex-ai-neuralink-2023-8%5C%22%3Escience%20fiction%20influences%3C%2Fa%3E%20throughout%20his%20life%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Douglas%20Adams'%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hitchhiker's%20Guide%20to%20the%20Galaxy%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20video%20game%20%26quot%3BDeus%20Ex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20mobile%20strategy%20game%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Battle%20of%20Polytopia%26quot%3B%20can%20now%20be%20added%20to%20the%20list.%20That's%20according%20to%C2%A0Walter%20Isaacson's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.simonandschuster.com%2Fbooks%2FElon-Musk%2FWalter-Isaacson%2F9781982181284%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20biography%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20detailed%20that%20the%20billionaire%20became%20obsessed%20with%20%26quot%3BPolytopia%26quot%3B%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20game%2C%20players%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20tribes%20waging%20war%20with%20each%20other%20to%20conquer%20the%20world%20of%20%26quot%3BPolytopia.%26quot%3B%20The%20game%20has%20been%20downloaded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fhl%3Den_AU%26id%3Dair.com.midjiwan.polytopia%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fhl%3Den_AU%26amp%3Bid%3Dair.com.midjiwan.polytopia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eover%2010%20million%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20Google%20Play%20store%20since%20it%20was%20released%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsaacson's%20book%20recounted%20two%20instances%20when%20Musk%20was%20so%20engrossed%20in%20the%20game%20that%20he%20once%20delayed%20a%20meeting%20with%20managers%20at%20Tesla's%20Berlin%20factory%20during%20a%20site%20visit%2C%20and%20even%20caused%20a%20fight%20with%20Grimes%20%E2%80%94%20whom%20he%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grimes-child-techno-mechanicus-tau-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20known%20children%20with%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20also%20played%20the%20game%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20Kimbal%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20ex-partner%20Grimes%2C%20and%20Shivon%20Zilis%2C%20a%20Neuralink%20director%20with%20whom%20Musk%20had%20twins%2C%20per%20the%20biography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKimbal%20told%20Isaacson%20he%20started%20playing%20the%20game%20to%20bond%20with%20his%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%20it%20would%20teach%20me%20how%20to%20be%20a%20CEO%20like%20he%20was.%20We%20called%20them%20Polytopia%20Life%20Lessons%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimbal%20added.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20eight%20CEO%20lessons%20that%20Elon%20handed%20down%20to%20his%20brother%20through%20the%20game%2C%20per%20Isaacson's%20conversations%20with%20Elon%2C%20Kimbal%2C%20Grimes%2C%20and%20Zilis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Empathy%20is%20not%20an%20asset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20that%20I%20have%20an%20empathy%20gene%2C%20unlike%20him%2C%20and%20it%20has%20hurt%20me%20in%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimbal%20told%20Isaacson%2C%20%26quot%3BPolytopia%20taught%20me%20how%20he%20thinks%20when%20you%20remove%20empathy.%20When%20you're%20playing%20a%20video%20game%2C%20there%20is%20no%20empathy%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Do%20not%20fear%20losing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20lose.%20It%20will%20hurt%20the%20first%20fifty%20times.%20When%20you%20get%20used%20to%20losing%2C%20you%20will%20play%20each%20game%20with%20less%20emotion%2C%26quot%3B%20Elon%20told%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Optimize%20every%20turn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20in%20Polytopia%2C%20you%20only%20get%20a%20set%20number%20of%20turns%20in%20life.%20If%20we%20let%20a%20few%20of%20them%20slide%2C%20we%20will%20never%20get%20to%20Mars%2C%26quot%3B%20Elon%20told%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Play%20life%20like%20a%20game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20book%2C%20Zilis%20once%20told%20Elon%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bthis%20feeling%20that%20as%20a%20kid%20you%20were%20playing%20one%20of%20these%20strategy%20games%20and%20your%20mom%20unplugged%20it%2C%20and%20you%20just%20didn't%20notice%2C%20and%20you%20kept%20playing%20life%20as%20if%20it%20were%20that%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Be%20proactive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZilis%20told%20Isaacson%20she%20received%20this%20advice%20while%20playing%20the%20game%20with%20Musk.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20little%20bit%20Canadian%20pacifist%20and%20reactive.%20My%20gameplay%20was%20a%20hundred%20percent%20reactive%20to%20what%20everyone%20else%20was%20doing%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20thinking%20through%20my%20best%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Double%20down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZilis%20further%20told%20Isaacson%20that%20Elon%20plays%20the%20game%20by%20pushing%20the%20edge%20of%20what's%20possible%20and%20that%20he's%20always%20doubling%20down%20and%20putting%20everything%20back%20in%20the%20game%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20just%20like%20he's%20just%20done%20his%20whole%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Zilis%20told%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3E7.%20Pick%20your%20battles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZilis%20also%20told%20Musk%20about%20not%20biting%20off%20more%20than%20he%20could%20chew%20in%20the%20game%2C%20per%20Isaacson's%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDude%2C%20like%2C%20everyone's%20swiping%20at%20you%20right%20now%2C%20but%20if%20you%20swipe%20back%20at%20too%20many%2C%20you'll%20run%20out%20of%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Unplug%20at%20times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKimbal%2C%20Zilis%2C%20and%20Grimes%20have%20since%20uninstalled%20the%20game%20%E2%80%94%20as%20did%20Elon%20for%20a%20time%2C%20according%20to%20Isaacson.%20Elon%20told%20Isaacson%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20take%20Polytopia%20off%20my%20phone%20because%20it%20was%20taking%20up%20too%20many%20brain%20cycles.%20I%20started%20dreaming%20about%20Polytopia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20Kimbal%20Musk%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ceo-lessons-brother-kimbal-polytopia-mobile-game-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650009af112d1600192d685e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ceo-lessons-brother-kimbal-polytopia-mobile-game-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHe%20said%20it%20would%20teach%20me%20how%20to%20be%20a%20CEO%20like%20he%20was%2C%20we%20called%20them%20Polytopia%20Life%20Lessons%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimbal%20Musk%20tol