y.%20IAF%20Mig%2029%20UPG%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fexercise-bright-star-23-indian-air-force-refuels-egyptian-rafale-fighters%2Farticleshow%2F103603060.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Government%20Headed%20for%20a%20Dal-Roti%20Mess%20as%20Traders%20Make%20a%20Killing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12124516%2Fangshu-purkait-UwdHrmoE0fU-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ELentils%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20have%20a%20peculiar%20relationship.%20In%20its%20first%20year%2C%20the%20government%20faced%20hyperinflation%20in%20dal%20prices%2C%20and%20now%2C%20over%20nine%20years%20later%2C%20India%20is%20once%20again%20grappling%20with%20imminent%20dal%20and%20food%20price%20inflation%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDal%20prices%20have%20already%20begun%20to%20rise%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20prompting%20hoarders%20and%20big%20traders%20to%20stockpile%20dals%20in%20their%20warehouses.%20The%20government%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%202015%20dal%20crisis%2C%20has%20been%20carefully%20managing%20the%20food%20economy%20through%20export%20and%20import%20bans%20and%20custom%20duties.%20But%20the%20recent%20government%20order%20concerning%20masoor%2C%20tur%20and%20chana%20dals%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%20wrote%20to%20all%20state%20chief%20secretaries%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20ensure%20that%20any%20available%20stocks%20of%20masoor%2C%20tur%20and%20urad%20dal%20with%20stockists%20in%20their%20respective%20states%20are%20declared%20on%20the%20government%20portal.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20all-India%20average%20price%20of%20tur%2Farhar%20dal%20has%20surged%2025%25%20to%20Rs%20128.66%20per%20kg%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20open%20up%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20there%20may%20be%20issues%20with%20importers%20as%20well.%20The%20government%20issued%20another%20clarification%2C%20requiring%20importers%20of%20pulses%20to%20compulsorily%20declare%20their%20available%20stocks.%20This%20step%20became%20necessary%20as%20several%20importers%20had%20been%20holding%20dal%20stocks%20after%20benefiting%20from%20relaxed%20import%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20government%20reduced%20import%20duties%20on%20dal%2C%20flooding%20the%20markets.%20But%20neither%20consumers%20nor%20farmers%20have%20benefited%20from%20this%20policy%20because%20importers%2C%20foreign%20traders%20and%20large%20stockholders%20have%20once%20again%20reaped%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20the%20imports%2C%20which%20is%20in%20their%20godowns.%20While%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20are%20commendable%2C%20they%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20curb%20dal%20price%20inflation.%20In%20fact%2C%20some%20measures%20may%20inadvertently%20favour%20these%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20the%20case%3F%20Firstly%2C%20the%20government%20allowed%20the%20cartel%20responsible%20for%20dal%20price%20manipulation%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20to%20go%20unpunished.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20attempted%20to%20dismantle%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%20as%20part%20of%20the%20farm%20laws.%20A%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0investigation%20initiated%20by%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20was%20closed%20for%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20two%20government%20departments%20could%20study%20the%20same%20problem%20and%20arrive%20at%20different%20conclusions.%20While%20the%20IT%20department%20found%20evidence%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccartelization%E2%80%9D%20and%20conducted%20an%20investigation%2C%20the%20CCI%20did%20not%20find%20sufficient%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELentils%20are%20a%20major%20protein%20source%20for%20most%20Indians%2C%20yet%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20hoarders%20or%20foreign%20corporations%20that%20openly%20profited%20from%20price%20manipulation%20in%202015.%20The%20same%20people%20are%20probably%20exploiting%20loopholes%20to%20profit%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20hunger%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20discuss%20dal%20import%20custom%20duties%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20G20.%20Lowering%20customs%20duties%20on%20US-origin%20lentils%20like%20chickpeas%20is%20a%20way%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa078b3f3-a773-4a6c-86e4-115800762a19%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa078b3f3-a773-4a6c-86e4-115800762a19%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1694575916243000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0TafU7XM6rX63qGhePUAhz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappease%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20US%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20exporters%20of%20lentils%20to%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20progressively%20reduced%20duties%20on%20US-origin%20lentils%20from%2030%25%20to%2020%25%2C%20and%20now%20to%20none.%20This%20move%20serves%20a%20dual%20purpose%3A%20it%20creates%20demand%20for%20cheap%20exports%20due%20to%20artificial%20scarcity%2C%20allows%20India%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ties%20with%20Biden%20and%20enables%20Modi%20to%20acquire%20US%20dal%20along%20with%20second-grade%20weapons%20systems.%20This%20pleases%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20electorate%2C%20benefits%20Modi%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C