and%20fails%20to%20control%20inflation%2C%20India%20will%20not%20remain%20silent%2C%20as%20this%20issue%20directly%20impacts%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edal-roti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20basic%20staple%20of%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20is%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks%E2%80%99.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694509244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12124516%2Fangshu-purkait-UwdHrmoE0fU-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-government-headed-for-a-dal-roti-mess-as-traders-make-a-killing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%202015%20dal%20crisis%2C%20has%20been%20carefully%20managing%20the%20food%20economy%20through%20export%20and%20import%20bans%20and%20custom%20duties.%20But%20a%20recent%20government%20order%20concerning%20masoor%2C%20tur%20and%20chana%20dals%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-government-headed-for-a-dal-roti-mess-as-traders-make-a-killing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Walmart%20customers%20either%20hate%20or%20love%20the%20chain's%20new%20shopping%20carts.%20We%20tried%20one%20out%2C%20and%20it's%20clear%20why%20they%20are%20so%20polarizing.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221373%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20traditional%20Walmart%20shopping%20cart%20next%20to%20the%20new%20design.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ff764d4b33390019f0c1af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22883%5C%22%3E%