emoved%20the%20super-hot%20tortilla%20chip%20from%20the%20sites%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Harris%20Wolobah%20in%20Massachusetts.%20Amazon%20said%20that%20it%20would%20remove%20the%20product%20from%20its%20sites%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Britain%2C%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa.%20It%20also%20plans%20to%20contact%20any%20international%20buyers%20who%20recently%20bought%20the%20chips%20to%20inform%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20eBay%20spokesperson%20said%20user%20safety%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Btop%20priority%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20had%20removed%20sale%20listings.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20monitoring%20our%20site%20closely%20and%20will%20remove%20any%20other%20listings%20if%20they%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsbeat-66753429%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cause%20of%20Harris%20Wolobah's%20death%20on%20September%201%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20confirmed%2C%20but%20his%20parents%20blame%20the%20'One%20Chip%20Challenge'.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencealert.com%2Fus-teen-dies-after-eating-notorious-spicy-chip-in-viral-challenge%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScience%20Alert%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2014-year-old%20was%20a%20healthy%20adolescent%20with%20no%20medical%20conditions%20that%20could%20easily%20explain%20any%20potential%20complications.%20Yet%20shortly%20after%20eating%20the%20tortilla%20chip%2C%20the%20boy%20visited%20his%20school%20nurse%20complaining%20of%20stomach%20pain.%20Within%20hours%20of%20being%20sent%20home%2C%20he%20passed%20out%20and%20stopped%20breathing%2C%20his%20family%20said.%20He%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20in%20spite%20of%20efforts%20by%20paramedics%20and%20hospital%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Harris'%20mother%20has%20called%20for%20the%20product%20to%20be%20withdrawn%20from%20sale.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20want%20there%20to%20be%20an%20awareness%20for%20parents%20to%20know%20that%20it's%20not%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20Lois%20Wolobah%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felon-musks-biography-here-are-5-big-revelations-from-the-book-4381836%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20Biography%3A%20Here%20Are%205%20Big%20Revelations%20From%20The%20Book%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnack-maker%20Paqui%20claims%20that%20the%20single%20tortilla%20contains%20a%20blend%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20hottest%20peppers%20available%26quot%3B.%20Millions%20of%20people%20have%20watched%20YouTubers%20and%20TikTokers%20attempt%20the%20viral%20dare%20and%20their%20extreme%20reactions%20to%20it.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20challenge%20has%20inspired%20a%20lot%20of%20teenagers%20to%20purchase%20the%20product%20to%20try%20it%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20following%20the%2014-year-old's%20death%2C%20the%20company%20on%20Thursday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpaquichips%2Fstatus%2F1699875802941145473%5C%22%3Eannounced%20its%20decision%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20remove%20stock%20from%20the%20stores.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20challenge%20was%20%26quot%3Bintended%20for%20adults%20only%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20for%20anyone%20with%20underlying%20health%20conditions%20or%20allergies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20said%20it%20had%20seen%20an%20%26quot%3Bincrease%20in%20teens%20and%20other%20individuals%20not%20heeding%20these%20warnings%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20while%20the%20product%20continues%20to%20adhere%20to%20food%20safety%20standards%2C%20out%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%2C%20we%20are%20actively%20working%20with%20our%20retailers%20to%20remove%20the%20product%20from%20shelves%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694503380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F19qp8e_one-chip-challen