Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpetitioner-in-sc-accuses-sebi-of-concealing-2014-dri-alert-on-adani%2Farticle67295917.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Anamika%20Jaiswal%2C%20represented%20by%20advocates%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20and%20Cheryl%20D%E2%80%99Souza%2C%20alleged%20that%20SEBI%20had%20%E2%80%9Cconcealed%20a%20January%202014%20DRI%20alert%20about%20Adani%20having%20siphoned%20off%20money%20and%20invested%20them%20in%20Adani%20listed%20companies%20through%20entities%20based%20in%20Dubai%20and%20Mauritius%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20claimed%20the%20DRI%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20then%20SEBI%20chairperson%2C%20U.K.%20Sinha%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%202014%2C%20alerting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20may%20be%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20being%20committed%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20companies%20using%20the%20money%20siphoned%20off%20through%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20power%20equipment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20DRI%20had%20sent%20a%20CD%2C%20containing%20evidence%20of%20siphoning%20of%20Rs%202%2C323%20crore%20and%20notes%20on%20the%20case%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20anti-smuggling%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-hhE_MfhZgY%5C%22%3Elatest%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20And%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20says%2C%20citing%20documents%2C%20which%20it%20also%20shared%20with%3Cem%3E%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Sinha%2C%20the%20then%20SEBI%20head%2C%20currently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fndtv-appoints-former-sebi-chairman-uk-sinha-as-non-executive-chairman-16279441.htm%5C%22%3Eserves%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20non-executive%20director%20of%20NDTV%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20SEBI%20has%20not%20disclosed%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20said%20letter%20(DRI%20letter)%20and%20evidence%20from%20the%20DRI%20till%20date%20before%20this%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20citing%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20previous%20statements%20to%20the%20top%20court%20that%20it%20started%20the%20investigation%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20only%20in%20June-July%202020%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20alleged%20that%20this%20was%20suppression%20of%20facts%20and%20providing%20false%20information%20which%20amounts%20to%20perjury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%202014%20DRI%20letter%2C%20the%20affidavit%20brought%20attention%20to%20numerous%20other%20key%20aspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConflict%20of%20interest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbreaking-sebi-concealed-2014-dri-alert-about-adani-group-manipulations-has-conflict-of-interest-petitioner-tells-supreme-court-237522%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20affidavit%20pointed%20out%20that%20Cyril%20Shroff%2C%20managing%20partner%2C%20Cyril%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%2C%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20committee%20on%20corporate%20governance%2C%20which%20looks%20at%20offences%20such%20as%20insider%20trading.%20Shroff%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20is%20married%20to%20Karan%20Adani%2C%20son%20of%20Gautam%20Adani.%20Hence%2C%20the%20relation%20causes%20the%20conflict%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20out%20of%2024%20SEBI%20investigation%20reports%20are%20on%20insider%20trading%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20companies%2C%20said%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmendments%20of%20the%20FPI%20regulations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulations%20initially%20mandated%20that%20designated%20depository%20participants%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20had%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPIs)%20did%20not%20maintain%20opaque%20structures.%20However%2C%20in%202018%2C%20SEBI%20revised%20this%20requirement%20by%20redefining%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98ultimate%20beneficial%20owners%E2%80%99%20to%20align%20with%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98beneficial%20owner%E2%80%99%20as%20defined%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20July%2011%20asked%20SEBI%20to%20explain%20why%20the%20law%20was%20tweaked%20in%202018%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20change%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsc-asks-sebi-why-changes-were-made-to-law-that-limited-its-ability-to-probe-opacity-in-fpi-ownership%5C%22%3Eis%20absolutely%20fatal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20current%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20SEBI%20repealed%20the%202014%20provisions%20on%20%E2%80%9Copaque%20structures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F6-out-of-8-offshore-funds-used-for-share-purchases-in-adani-firms-shut-down-amid-allegations%5C%22%3E6%20Out%20of%208%20Offshore%20Funds%20Used%20for%20Share%20Purchases%20in%20Adani%20Firms%20Shut%20Down%20Amid%20Probe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20the%20changes%20significant%3F%20Because%20the%20Supreme%20Court-led%20expert%20committee%20was%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20if%20there%20was%20violation%20of%20the%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%2C%20or%20free%20float%2C%20norms%20by%20the%20Adani%20group.%20Hindenburg%20Research%20alleged%20that%20overseas%20entities%20and%20shell%20companies%20that%20were%20tied%20to%20Adani%20group%20%E2%80%9Csurreptitiously%E2%80%9D%20owned%20stock%20in%20its%20listed%20firms.%20This%20indicated%20a%20violation%20of%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20free%20float%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublicly%20traded%20companies%20are%20required%20to%20have%20at%20least%2025%25%20of%20their%20shares%20held%20by%20non-promoters%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20retail%20investors%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20FPIs%2C%20and%20insurance%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20to%20stay%20listed%20on%20exchanges.%20These%20shares%20are%20called%20public%20float%20or%20free%20float%20or%20public%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20listed%20is%20critical%20as%20it%20allows%20a%20company%20to%20raise%20money%20from%20the%20market.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20these%20rules%20are%20not%20met%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-vinod-adani-free-float-rules%5C%22%3Eimplications%20on%20these%20companies%E2%80%99%20public%20listing%20status.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefinition%20of%20related%20party%20amended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20SEBI%20Listing%20Obligations%20and%20Disclosure%20Requirement%20(LODR)%2C%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98related%20party%E2%80%99%20was%20originally%20defined%20to%20align%20with%20the%20definition%20provided%20in%20Section%202(76)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20However%2C%20in%202018%2C%20SEBI%20made%20an%20amendment%20to%20this%20definition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20amendment%20introduced%20a%20separate%20provision%20that%20enabled%20a%20member%20or%20entity%20of%20the%20promoter%20group%20of%20a%20listed%20company%20as%20a%20related%20party%20only%20if%20the%20shareholding%20of%20that%20person%20was%20at%20least%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694502918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsebi-concealed-dri-letter-on-stock-market-manipulation-by-adani-group-in-2014-petitioner-to-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20addition%20to%20the%202014%20DRI%20letter%2C%20the%20affidavit%20brought%20attention%20to%20numerous%20other%20key%20issues%20such%20as%20amendments%20to%20FPI%20regulations%20by%20the%20markets%20regulator%20in%202018%20and%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhushan%3A%20'Animal'%20will%20be%20a%20Pan%20world%20film%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694502877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103599929%2Cimgsize-16366.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanimal-producer-bhushan-kumar-says-the-ranbir-kapoor-starrer-will-be-a-pan-world-film%2Farticleshow%2F103599959.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103599959.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EProducer%20Bhushan%20Kumar%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20upcoming%20film%20'Animal'%2C%20starring%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3BPan%20World%20Film%26quot%3B.%20He%20expressed%20his%20excitement%20for%20the%20project%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20will%20offer%20drama%2C%20action%2C%20and%20emotions%2C%20with%20remarkable%20performances%20from%20actors%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20Anil%20Kapoor%2C%20and%20Bobby%20Deol.%20The%20pre-teaser%20of%20the%20film%20received%20positive%20feedback%2C%20and%20the%20teaser%20is%20planned%20to%20be%20released%20on%20Ranbir's%20birthday.%20Bhushan%20Kumar%20also%20discussed%20other%20pro