t.%20All%20the%20senior%20professors%20who%20sympathised%20with%20Sinha%20and%20were%20convinced%20of%20the%20plagiarism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roundtableindia.co.in%2Fdr-sarvepalli-radhakrishnan-the-teacher-who-plagiarised-his-student-s-thesis%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20refused%20to%20stand%20as%20a%20witness%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20him%20in%20the%20court.%20Sinha%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20fight%20a%20prolonged%20legal%20battle%20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Radhakrishnan%20had%20both%20financial%20and%20social%20capital%20to%20manipulate%2C%20manage%20and%20obtain%20the%20help%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20especially%20that%20of%20Shyamaprasad%20Mukherjee%2C%20son%20of%20Sir%20Ashutosh%20Mukheriee.%20It%20was%20Sir%20Ashutosh%20Mukheriee%2C%20the%20then%20vice%20chancellor%20of%20Calcutta%20University%2C%20who%20had%20brought%20Radhakrishnan%20from%20Bangalore%20to%20Calcutta%20University%20for%20the%20prestigious%20post%20of%20King%20George%20V%20Professorship%20on%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201000%20per%20month.%20His%20son%2C%20Shyamaprasad%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Dr.%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20therefore%2C%20wanted%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20book%20on%20Radhakirishnan%E2%80%99s%20plagiarism%2C%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Reported%20case%20of%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20Literary%20Piracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Barin%20De%2C%20based%20on%20the%20documents%20submitted%20by%20Sinha%20in%20the%20court%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcat.org%2Ftitle%2Freported-case-of-radhakrishnans-literary-piracy%2Foclc%2F56322949%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econveniently%20vanished%20from%20the%20libraries%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Aich.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20plagiarism%20allegations%20against%20Radhakrishnan%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20his%20legacy%20as%20an%20educator%20and%20philosopher.%20Such%20accusations%20not%20only%20question%20the%20integrity%20of%20a%20celebrated%20figure%20but%20also%20challenge%20the%20principles%20of%20academic%20honesty%20and%20authenticity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAside%20from%20the%20plagiarism%20allegations%2C%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20women%20have%20also%20raised%20eyebrows.%20He%20believed%20that%20the%20role%20of%20women%20was%20best%20fulfilled%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20marriage%20and%20motherhood.%20Notably%2C%20Radhakrishnan%20arranged%20the%20marriages%20of%20his%20daughters%20without%20their%20consent%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20were%20married%20off%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20biography%20written%20by%20his%20son%20Sarvepalli%20Gopal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20juxtaposition%20of%20his%20traditional%20views%20on%20women%20with%20his%20celebrated%20role%20as%20an%20educator%2C%20then%2C%20seem%20hypocritical.%20Celebrating%20a%20figure%20who%20held%20such%20views%20as%20the%20symbol%20of%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%20may%20send%20the%20wrong%20message%20about%20the%20values%20that%20educators%20should%20uphold%2C%20including%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnother%20contender%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESavitribai%20Phule%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20educating%20girls%2C%20especially%20girls%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds%2C%20was%20revolutionary%20not%20only%20for%20her%20time%20but%20even%20today.%20Her%20unwavering%20dedication%20to%20breaking%20the%20barriers%20of%20caste%20and%20gender%2C%20along%20with%20her%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20provide%20education%20to%20those%20who%20were%20denied%20it%2C%20make%20her%20a%20true%20icon%20of%20education%20and%20social%20reform.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20important%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20Phule%20existed%20almost%20a%20century%20before%20Radhakrishnan%20and%20her%20ideas%20were%20centuries%20ahead%20of%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FSavitribai_Phule1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20portrait%20of%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22201%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-62063%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20portrait%20of%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhule%E2%80%99s%20extraordinary%20contributions%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20female%20teacher%20and%20her%20relentless%20efforts%20in%20fighting%20caste-based%20discrimination%20make%20her%20an%20ideal%20choice%20to%20honour%20on%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day.%20She%20embodies%20the%20true%20spirit%20of%20education%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20for%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20day%20to%20be%20celebrated%20on%20January%203%20i.e.%20Savitribai%20Phule%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20instead%20of%20on%20September%205%2C%20in%20my%20humble%20opinion%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20to%20be%20made.%20A%20better%20birthday%20to%20commemorate%20and%20honour%20the%20true%20spirit%20and%20significance%20of%20a%20teacher%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20on%20the%20subcontinent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhule%20is%20considered%20the%20pioneer%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20feminist%20movement%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20education%20in%20India.%20She%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20Jyotiba%20Phule%2C%20started%20the%20first%20modern%20day%20school%20for%20girls%20in%201848%20in%20Pune%20%E2%80%93%20at%20a%20time%20when%20girls%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20school%2C%20in%20Bhide%20Wada%2C%20which%20has%20so%20far%20existed%20in%20shambles%2C%20is%20only%20now%2C%20in%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpune%2Fbhide-wada-to-be-national-monument-foundation-stone-in-2-months-maharashtra-cm-eknath-shinde%2Farticleshow%2F96722407.cms%5C%22%3Ebeing%20considered%20to%20be%20deemed%20as%20a%20heritage%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20redeveloped%20as%20a%20national%20monument.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20husband-wife%20duo%20opened%2018%20schools%20for%20children%20of%20different%20castes%20and%20established%20two%20educational%20trusts%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Native%20Female%20School%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20the%20Society%20for%20Promoting%20the%20Education%20of%20Mahars%2C%20Mangs%20and%20others.%20They%20also%20opened%20a%20care%20center%20called%20Balhatya%20Pratibandhak%20Griha%20for%20children%20who%20were%20victims%20of%20rape%2C%20sati%20and%20those%20who%20escaped%20female%20infanticide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESavitribai%20was%20the%20first%20woman%20in%20modern%20India%20to%20challenge%20the%20work%20prescribed%20for%20Hindu%20women%20by%20the%20scriptures%20n%2C%20social%20system%20and%20tradition%20for%20Shudra-Ati%20Shudras.%20She%20fought%20all%20her%20life%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20Shudra-Ati%20Shudras%20and%20the%20liberation%20of%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Phules%20stood%20as%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20Brahmanism%20and%20the%20road%20to%20ending%20their%20monopoly%20was%20paved%20with%20difficulty.%20The%20privileged%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20Brahmin%20class%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%20harassed%20the%20Phules%20because%20they%20belonged%20to%20the%20oppressed%20Mali%20caste.%20On%20her%20way%20to%20school%2C%20Savitribai%20was%20abused%20and%20had%20dung%20thrown%20at%20her.%20She%20simply%20changed%20into%20a%20spare%20saree%20she%20always%20carried%20with%20her%20and%20continued%20on%20her%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FPhule-edited.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FPhule-edited.jpeg%20796w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FPhule-edited-300x148.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-23748%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBusts%20of%20Mahatma%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20and%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20eventually%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jagranjosh.com%2Fgeneral-knowledge%2Famp%2Fsavitribai-phule-biography-husband-children-work-for-girls-education-schools-awards-death-1641193310-1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eforced%20to%20leave%20Jyotiba%E2%80%99s%20father%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%201849%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20committing%20the%20sin%20of%20studying%20against%20Manusmriti%20and%20its%20Brahmanical%20texts.%20Given%20the%20monopoly%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20over%20all%20resources%20in%20this%20country%2C%20especially%20education%20and%20the%20access%20it%20can%20provide%2C%20one%20must%20really%20sit%20and%20question%20why%20we%20think%20%E2%80%98Teacher%E2%80%99s%20day%E2%80%99%20and%20its%20celebration%20should%20be%20one%20that%20commemorates%20Brahmanism%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20inhuman%20exclusionary%20spirit%20that%20to%20this%20day%20marginalises%20such%20a%20vast%20population%20of%20this%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brahminical%20idea%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98teacher%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98guru%E2%80%99%2C%20that%20glorifies%20the%20ideas%20of%20authority%20and%20respect%20over%20the%20well%20being%20and%20democratisation%20of%20knowledge%2C%20that%20upholds%20the%20varna%20system%20and%20assigns%20occupations%20by%20birth%20and%20justifies%20who%20is%20worthy%20of%20knowledge%20and%20who%20is%20not%20is%20simply%20a%20heartless%20and%20cruel%20system%20of%20discrimination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dalit-students-suicides-in-two-months-highlight-institutionalised-discrimination-at-iits%5C%22%3Ekillings%20by%20suicide%20of%20students%20from%20SC%2FST%20backgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20premiere%20institutes%20is%20rampant%20because%20of%20the%20very%20Brahmanical%20nature%20of%20education%20in%20this%20country%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20and%20emulate%20Savitribai%20and%20what%20she%20fought%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dalit-students-suicides-in-two-months-highlight-institutionalised-discrimination-at-iits%5C%22%3ETwo%20Dalit%20Students%E2%80%99%20Suicides%20in%20Two%20Months%20Highlight%20%E2%80%98Institutionalised%20Discrimination%E2%80%99%20at%20IITs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETeacher%E2%80%99s%20day%20should%20be%20about%20teachers%20who%20go%20against%20the%20grain%2C%20who%20fight%20injustice%20everyday%2C%20who%20crush%20hierarchies%2C%20who%20make%20education%20the%20tool%20of%20liberation%20that%20it%20can%20be%20and%20not%20about%20teachers%20who%20are%20plagiarists%2C%20who%20steal%20from%20their%20own%20students%20and%20further%20regressive%20views.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20a%20tradition%20in%20this%20country%2C%20to%20glorify%20Brahmin-Baniya%20men%2C%20to%20shower%20them%20with%20laurels%20and%20to%20celebrate%20them%20to%20no%20end%2C%20to%20forgive%20and%2