tion%20parties%20in%20Kashmir%20have%20urged%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janta%20Party-led%20Union%20government%20to%20roll%20back%20the%20decision%20while%20local%20stakeholders%20are%20anguished%20that%20the%20waiver%20will%20negatively%20impact%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20apple%20industry%2C%20which%20employs%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20people%20directly%20and%20indirectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20of%20tariff%2C%20which%20has%20chopped%20off%20extra%2020%25%20from%20the%2070%25%20tariff%20imposed%20since%202019%20by%20New%20Delhi%20on%20the%20premium%20Washington%20apples%2C%20was%20announced%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20September%205%20when%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20reportedly%20released%20a%20notification%20ahead%20of%20the%20meeting%20between%20Modi%20and%20his%20US%20counterpart%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G-20%20Summit%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20announced%20the%20tax%20waiver%20on%20several%20US%20products%20such%20as%20walnuts%2C%20lentils%2C%20chickpeas%20and%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fg20-farmers-agriculture-bio-fuel-india-us%5C%22%3EThe%20G20%20Has%20Summarily%20Failed%20to%20Address%20Agrarian%20Distress%20in%20its%20Member%20Countries%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kashmir-based%20traders%20and%20growers%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Washington%20apples%20with%20a%20tax%20waiver%20into%20the%20market%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20set%20to%20pick%20up%20will%20lead%20to%20pricing%20fluctuations%20which%20will%20hit%20the%20local%20industry%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Kashmiris%20put%20in%20agony%20only%20to%20receive%20applause%20from%20foreign%20countries%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh%20inflation%20has%20already%20led%20to%20a%20shoot%20up%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20apple%20production%20while%20the%20yield%20has%20also%20fallen%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20tax%20waiver%20%5Bon%20imported%20US%20apples%5D%20will%20hit%20not%20just%20the%20farmers%20of%20Kashmir%20but%20also%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand.%20The%20government%20should%20reconsider%20the%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bashir%20Ahmad%20Bashir%2C%20president%20of%20the%20All%20Valley%20Fruit%20Growers%20and%20Dealers%20Association%20(AVFGDA)%2C%20the%20leading%20association%20of%20apple%20growers%20and%20traders%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20function%20here%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20called%20for%20a%20rollback%20of%20the%20waiver%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Creflects%20the%20disconnect%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20imported%20apples%2C%20walnuts%20or%20almonds%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20government%20is%20increasing%20hardships%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20order%20to%20please%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries.%20Kashmiris%20are%20put%20in%20agony%20only%20to%20receive%20applause%20from%20the%20foreign%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20the%20import%20tariff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmir%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20apple%20basket%2C%20producing%20around%2021%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20fruit%20last%20year%20(or%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20apples%20produced%20in%20India)%20which%20generates%20a%20revenue%20of%20between%20Rs%2010%2C000-Rs%2014%2C000%20crore%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20horticulture%20sector%20contributes%20around%20eight%20to%2010%25%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20were%20caught%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20when%2C%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Washington%20raised%20tariffs%20by%2010-25%25%20on%20specific%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20items%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20concerns.%20India%20followed%20suit%20by%20increasing%20tariffs%20on%20several%20US%20products%2C%20including%20Washington%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imposition%20of%20extra%20tariff%20drastically%20reduced%20India%E2%80%99s%20apple%20imports%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20From%20US%20%24145.2%20million%20in%202018-19%20when%20the%20country%20imported%20US%20%24305.71%20million%20worth%20of%20apples%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data%2C%20the%20apple%20imports%20dropped%20to%20only%20US%20%245.27%20million%20in%202022-23%20when%20the%20total%20apple%20imports%20were%20at%20US%20%24295.94%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20Turkey%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20leading%20apple%20supplier%20for%20India%2C%20making%20up%20for%20more%20than%2084%25%20of%20total%20apple%20imports%20followed%20by%20Italy%2C%20Chile%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20harvest%20season%20picking%20up%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20premium%20quality%20Washington%20apples%20in%20the%20market%2C%20which%20are%20wax-polished%20to%20increase%20their%20shelf%20life%2C%20has%20dampened%20the%20spirits%20of%20local%20growers%20and%20traders%2C%20who%20were%20hoping%20to%20capitalise%20on%20low%20domestic%20production%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20suffered%20between%2040-50%25%20loss%20of%20apple%20produce%20due%20to%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20hailstorms%20and%20flood%20which%20led%20to%20spread%20of%20diseases%20such%20as%20scab%20and%20powdery%20mildew%20in%20apple%20trees%20and%20immature%20fruit%20droppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Pexels%2Frohitsinghprashar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Waiver%20will%20narrow%20down%20price%20difference%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20traders%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Delicious%20variety%2C%20which%20makes%2070-80%25%20of%20total%20apples%20produced%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20sold%20for%20around%20Rs%2075%20per%20kilogram%20in%20the%20wholesale%20market%20last%20year.%20One%20box%20of%20Kashmiri%20Red%20Delicious%20apples%2C%20which%20contains%20around%2020%20kilograms%20of%20fruit%2C%20fetches%20Rs%201%2C200-1%2C500%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Azadpur%20Mandi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20fruit%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20a%20kilo%20of%20the%20imported%20US%20apples%20sold%20for%20around%20Rs%20120%20in%20the%20wholesale%20market%20of%20Azadpur%20Mandi%2C%20according%20to%20a%20trader.%20A%2032-kg%20box%20sold%20for%20Rs%203%2C000-4%2C000%20last%20year%20while%20a%2025-kg%20box%20fetched%20Rs%202%2C500-3%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20of%20tariff%20will%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20bright-red%20and%20glossy%20Washington%20apples%20in%20wholesale%20markets%20to%20Rs%20100%20a%20kilo%2C%20making%20them%20a%20direct%20and%20more%20powerful%20competitor%20for%20local%20apple%20varieties%20which%20are%20dull%20in%20colour%20and%20also%20lack%20lustre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20waiver%20will%20narrow%20down%20the%20price%20difference%20between%20imported%20and%20local%20apples.%20The%20quality%20of%20imported%20apples%20is%20exceptionally%20high%20and%20our%20apples%20don%E2%80%99t%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20front%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghulam%20Jeelani%20Dar%2C%20an%20apple%20trader%20from%20central%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Ashraf%20Wani%2C%20a%20grower%20from%20Shopian%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20apple%20producing%20districts%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20US%20are%20more%20advanced%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20use%20of%20farming%20technologies%20and%20the%20subsidies%20provided%20by%20their%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20waiver%20on%20tariff%20will%20hit%20both%20growers%20and%20traders%20in%20India%20equally%20as%20the%20domestic%20varieties%20of%20apples%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20Washington%20apple%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wani%2C%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Shopian%20Fruit%20Mandi%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20traders%20believe%20that%20the%20local%20varieties%20of%20apples%20will%20be%20equally%20in%20high%20demand%20due%20to%20low%20production%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20waiver%20will%20not%20lower%20the%20prices%20of%20local%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20for%20apples%20is%20high%20this%20year%20due%20to%20low%20production.%20Thus%20the%20tariff%20waiver%20on%20imported%20apples%20will%20not%20have%20any%20significant%20impact%20on%20local%20producers%20and%20traders%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravinder%20Chauhan%2C%20president%20of%C2%A0%C2%A0Apple%20Growers%20Association%20of%20India%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuty%20policy%20and%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imposes%2035%25%20duty%20and%2015%25%20cess%20on%20apple%20imports%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20tariff%20to%2050%25%20of%20cost%2C%20but%20the%20tariff%20was%20set%20at%2070%25%20in%20case%20of%20the%20US%20apples%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20to%20waive%20off%2020%25%20tariff%20came%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20announced%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20free%20import%20of%20apples%20if%20the%20cost%2C%20insurance%20and%20freight%20(CIF)%20price%20was%20less%20than%20or%20equal%20to%20Rs%2050%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20was%20rolled%20out%20after%20underpriced%20apples%20from%20Iran%20made%20their%20way%20into%20Indian%20markets%20through%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20second%20country%20alongside%20Nepal%20to%20enjoy%20duty-free%20trade%20with%20India%2C%20putting%20the%20local%20growers%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20on%20the%20back-foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reports%20of%20many%20growers%20struggling%20to%20recover%20the%20production%20costs%20due%20to%20significantly%20low%20prices%20of%20imported%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImporting%20apples%20is%20not%20a%20wise%20policy%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wani%2C%20the%20trade%20leader%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20home%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20one-fourth%20population%2C%20our%20country%20is%20sufficient%20to%20consume%20the%20local%20production.%20While%20the%20government%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20increase%20tax%20duty%20to%20avoid%20any%20trade%20issues%20with%20the%20US%2C%20it%20can%20increase%20the%20cess%20on%20imported%20apples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Japan%20can%20impose%20100%25%20cess%20on%20rice%20imports%20to%20protect%20local%20farmers%2C%20what%20stops%20the%20Union%20government%20from%20taking%20a%20similar%20decision%3F%20The%20increase%20in%20cess%20will%20provide%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20both%20local%20and%20imported%20apples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWani%20believes%20that%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20invoke%20CIF%20price%20tag%20on%20imported%20apples%20because%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20tax%20revenue%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20calculated%20decision%20to%20prevent%20tax%20pilferage%20rather%20than%20a%20decision%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20indeed%20concerned%20about%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20apple%20farmers%2C%20it%20should%20announce%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20and%20crop%20insurance%20scheme%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Wani%2C%20the%20grower%20from%20Shopian.%20CIF%20or%20%E2%80%98cost%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20freight%E2%80%99%20are%20charges%20paid%20by%20a%20seller%20for%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBashir%2C%20the%20AVFGDA%20president%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20impose%20100%25%20import%20duty%20on%20imported%20apples%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20protect%20the%20local%20growers%2C%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%20apple%20farming%20will%20become%20an%20unsustainable%20practice%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeoples%20Democratic%20Party%20President%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20took%20to%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20urging%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20GOI%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20remove%20additional%20duties%20on%20apples%2C%20walnuts%2C%20and%20almonds%20will%20have%20a%20devastating%20effect%20on%20local%20growers%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20who%20are%20already%20grappling%20with%20huge%20losses%20since%202019.%20I%20hope%20%40PMOIndia%20reconsiders%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694500670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12115853%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fkashmir-apple-import-tariff-reduction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Kashmir-based%20traders%20and%20growers%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Washington%20apples%20with%20a%20tax%20waiver%20into%20the%20market%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20set%20to%20pick%20up%20will%20lead%20to%20pricing%20fluctuations%20which%20will%20hit%20the%20local%20industry%20badly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fkashmir-apple-import-tariff-reduction%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kareena%20reveals%20THIS%20about%20Taimur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694500641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103598591%2Cimgsize-27322.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-says-taimur-doesnt-like-being-clicked-by-the-paparazzi-reveals-what-saif-ali-khan-suggested-they-do%2Farticleshow%2F103598634.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103598634.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20reveals%20the%20reason%20why%20she%20or%20Saif%20never%20tried%20to%20cover%20the%20face%20of%20their%20kids%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20photographers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-says-taimur-doesnt-like-being-clicked-by-the-paparazzi-reveals-what-saif-ali-khan-suggested-they-do%2Farticleshow%2F103598634.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Football%20Team%20Picked%20On%20Basis%20Of%20Astrologer's%20Suggestions%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20sensational%20claim%20has%20rocked%20the%20Indian%20sporting%20fraternity%2C%20with%20a%20report%20claiming%20that%20the%20national%20football%20team's%20squad%20was%20picked%20by%20head%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20astrologer's%20suggestion.%20Stimac%20is%20said%20to%20have%20shared%20players'%20data%20with%20an%20astrologer%2C%20who%20responded%20by%20picking%20the%20names%20of%20players%20who%20were%20recommended%20for%20a%20particular%20day%20and%20those%20who%20should%20be%20avoided.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20report%20claims%20that%20the%20head%20coach%20was%20put%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20astrologer%20by%20the%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20general-secretary%20Kushal%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorried%20whether%20the%20Indian%20team%20would%20qualify%20for%20the%20Asian%20Cup%2C%20Das%20sought%20an%20astrologer's%20help%20and%20put%20him%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20team%2C%20Stimac.%20As%20names%20were%20shared%20by%20Stimac%20with%20the%20Astrologer%2C%20responses%20of%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%3B%20%26quot%3Bcan%20do%20very%20well.%20Needs%20to%20avoid%20overconfidence%26quot%3B%3B%20%26quot%3Ba%20below-average%20day%26quot%3B%3B%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20good%20day%20for%20him%20but%20might%20get%20over%20aggressive%26quot%3B%3B%20%26quot%3Bnot%20recommended%20for%20the%20day%26quot%3B%20came%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Ffootball%2Fasian-cup-prelims-india-football-coach-gave-details-of-players-to-astrologer-picked-team-on-his-advice-8935614%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claims%20that%20about%20100%20messages%20were%20exchanged%20between%20Stimac%20and%20the%20astrologer%20between%20May%20and%20June%20last%20year.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20India%20played%20a%20friendly%20against%20Jordan%20as%20well%20as%20three%20Asian%20Cup%20qualifiers%2C%20against%20Cambodia%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20messages%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report%2C%20didn't%20just%20feature%20inputs%20over%20selection%20matters%20in%20the%20team%20but%20also%20saw%20Stimac%20discuss%20injury%20news%20and%20substitution%20strategies%20with%20the%20astrologer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHi%20dear%20Bhupesh%2C%20it%20was%20a%20pleasure%20meeting%20you%20and%20discussing%20future%20work!%20I%20would%20kindly%20ask%20you%20to%20provide%20opinion%20on%20the%20following%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20messages%20read%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20game%20against%20Jordan%2C%20Stimac%20allegedly%20sought%20advice%20over%20the%20selection%20of%20an%20attacking%20midfielder.%20After%20the%20astrologer%20gave%20his%20preference%20of%20selection%2C%20Stimac%20is%20said%20to%20have%20gone%20with%20the%20inputs%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Kushal%20Das%20admitted%20that%20he%20put%20Stimac%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20astrologer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20met%20him%20at%20a%20meeting.%20He%20(Sharma)%20had%20worked%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20telecom%20companies%20and%20Bollywood%20personalities.%20What%20they%20presented%20was%20that%20astrological%20timings%20and%20the%20current%20phase%20of%20players%20can%20help%20motivate%20people%20into%20taking%20the%20right%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20told%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20time%2C%20I%20was%20worried%20if%20India%20would%20qualify%20for%20the%20Asian%20Cup%20and%20so%20was%20Igor%2C%20let%20me%20be%20very%20honest.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20comfortable%20situation.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20was%20that%20India%20should%20qualify.%20So%20I%20told%20him%20(Sharma)%20that%20I%20will%20put%20you%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20coach%20and%20if%20he%20likes%20it%2C%20he%20thinks%20your%20services%20can%20be%20utilised%2C%20he%20can%20get%20back%20to%20me.%20Igor%20was%20very%20convinced%20and%20they%20were%20in%20Kolkata%20throughout%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDas%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20astrologer%20was%20paid%20INR%2012-15%20lakh%20for%20his%20services%20over%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694500560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2Fo8trnp1o_stimac-instagram_650x300_02_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findian-football-team-picked-on-basis-of-astrologers-suggestions-to-coach-igor-stimac-report-4381972%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20a%20report%2C%20the%20Indian%20football%20team%20was%20picked%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20astrologer's%20suggestions%20last%20year.%20The%20astrologer%20gave%20inputs%20to%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%20based%20on%20the%20player%20information%20he%20received.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findian-football-team-picked-on-basis-of-astrologers-suggestions-to-coach-igor-stimac-report-4381972%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findian-football-team-picked-on-basis-of-astrologers-suggestions-to-coach-igor-stimac-report-4381972%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findian-football-team-picked-on-basis-of-astrologers-suggestions-to-coach-igor-stimac-report-4381972%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Hansal%20Mehta%20directing%20Saroj%20Khan's%20biopic%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694500448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103598479%2Cimgsize-52330.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%