2022%2C%20asked%20the%20deputy%20commissioners%20of%20the%20districts%20concerned%20to%20rectify%20the%20list%20of%20around%20400%20hill%20villages%20overlapping%20between%20the%20districts%20of%20Kakching%2C%20Tengnoupal%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20Bishnupur%2C%20the%20NCST%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20was%20prepared%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Estate%20review%20of%20Manipur%20conducted%20in%20December%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20which%20the%20NCST%20team%20met%20with%20Manipur%20government%20officials%20and%20representatives%20from%20the%20All%20Tribal%20Students%20Union%20Manipur%20(ATSUM)%20and%20the%20Joint%20Coordination%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Rights%20in%20Imphal%20(JCCOTR).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20a%20review%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20(AFSPA)%2C%201958%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20hill%20areas%20since%20the%20Act%20had%20been%20withdrawn%20from%2015%20police%20stations%20in%20the%20valley%20districts%2C%20calling%20its%20selective%20implementation%20%E2%80%9Cdiscriminatory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENCST%20had%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20reserve%20forests%2C%20including%20pocket%20settlements%2C%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20were%20moved%20to%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district%20in%20October%202022%20by%20the%20revenue%20department%20without%20specific%20approval%20from%20the%20Hill%20Areas%20Committee%20(HAC).%20The%20report%20recommended%20that%20this%20order%20should%20be%20reviewed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20representation%2C%20the%20ATSUM%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Meitei%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20ST%20status%20was%20an%20alleged%20attempt%20to%20grab%20tribal%20land.%20It%20noted%20that%20about%20144%20hill%20villages%20had%20been%20placed%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20police%20stations%20in%20valley%20districts%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20name%20of%20convenient%20administration%E2%80%9D%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Csystematic%20way%20of%20encroaching%20into%20hill%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ATSUM%20had%20also%20added%20that%20several%20hill%20villages%20had%20their%20land%20records%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20adjacent%20valley%20districts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tribal%20bodies%20also%20told%20the%20NCST%20of%20complaints%20about%20the%20majority%20Meitei%2FManipuri%20language%20being%20imposed%20on%20people%20from%20tribal%20communities%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ATSUM%20alleged%20that%20recruitment%20in%20banking%20institutions%20and%20postal%20services%20in%20the%20state%20required%20proof%20of%20passing%20Meitei%2FManipuri%20language%20class%20at%20the%20level%20of%20Class%20X%20or%20XII%2C%20when%20most%20ST%20students%20either%20opt%20for%20English%20or%20their%20traditional%20language%20at%20that%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20policies%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%20and%20discriminatory%E