anathan%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20at%20the%20budget-management%20company%20Coupa%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20had%20been%20designed%20to%20respond%20relatively%20quickly%20to%20market%20conditions%20like%20shifting%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20climate%20crisis%20presents%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20unpredictability%2C%20one%20that%20Viswanathan%C2%A0said%20could%20require%20predictive%20weather%20analysis%20using%20algorithms%20and%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20shipper%20paid%20over%20%242%20million%20to%20cross%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20could%20hit%20consumer%20prices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProject44%2C%20a%20supply-chain%20platform%2C%20told%20Insider%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20the%20drought%20conditions%20had%20caused%20shipping%20capacity%20through%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20to%20drop%20by%20over%2020%25%20in%20the%20prior%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20is%20concerning%2C%20as%20it%20is%20peak%20shipping%20season%20when%20retailers%20ramp%20up%20shipping%20in%20anticipation%20of%20increased%20demand%20ahead%20of%20holiday%20shopping.%20About%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltrademag.com%2Fpotential-shortages-loom-as-panama-canal-restrictions-impact-holiday-stocks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40%25%20of%20US%20container%20traffic%3C%2Fa%3E%20passes%20through%20the%20waterway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20downward%20trend%20continues%2C%20it%20could%20prompt%20shippers%20to%20reevaluate%20their%20choice%20of%20ports%20for%20bringing%20in%20inventory%20to%20ensure%20holiday%20season%20shelves%20remain%20adequately%20stocked%2C%26quot%3B%20Project44%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20has%20the%20shipping%20giant%20Maersk%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20low%20water%20levels%20at%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20are%20a%20clear%20example%20of%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20in%20rain