0is%20troubling%20because%20it%20adds%20to%20the%20existing%20stress%20on%20the%20world's%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20China's%20strict%20on-off%20lockdowns%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20underscored%20the%20risks%20of%20depending%20so%20heavily%20on%20the%20East%20Asian%20country%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20world's%20factory%20floor%20for%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20was%20the%20tech%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-accelerates-production-china-protests-2022-12%5C%22%3EApple%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20supply-chain%20disruptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20China's%20COVID-19%20containment%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20accelerated%20a%20global%20supply-chain%20diversification%20away%20from%20China%20that%20kicked%20off%20in%20about%202018%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22b395ea199b0825a4787b214170b628c7%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Feconomy%2Fchina-economy%2Farticle%2F3146489%2Fus-china-trade-war-timeline-key-dates-and-events-july-2018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20war%20against%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Ftimeline%2Fus-china-relations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington-Beijing%20tensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20still%20high%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20area%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fus-investors-flag-retaliation-risks-after-bidens-china-tech-curbs-2023-08-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-tech%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prompting%20investors%20across%20the%20board%20to%20reconsider%20their%20business%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E