uch%20longer%20for%20some%20models.%20Deutsche%20Bank%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%2C%20though%2C%20that%20a%20strike%20could%20influence%20each%20automaker's%20earnings%20by%20%24400%20million%20to%20%24500%20million%20for%20each%20week%20of%20lost%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20automakers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautomakers-car-buyers-investors-inventory-strike-pricing-incentives-electric-vehicles-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efaced%20supply-chain%20constraints%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20with%20computer%20chips%2C%20that%20hindered%20vehicle%20production.%20Despite%20a%20lack%20of%20inventory%2C%20industry%20profits%20skyrocketed%2C%20even%20though%202022%20was%20the%20worst%20year%20for%20sales%20for%20the%20auto%20industry%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UAW%20strike%20could%20damage%20the%20Fed's%20progress%20in%20bringing%20inflation%20down%20to%20its%202%25%20target.%20Inflation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-inflation-economy-cpi-july-data-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20about%203.2%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%20August.%20New-vehicle%20prices%20may%20increase%20nearly%202%25%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20two-week%20strike%2C%20the%20automotive-consulting%20firm%20J.D.%20Power%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Fpotential-uaw-strike-could-cut-production-push-up-vehicle-prices-analysts-say-2023-09-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20may%20stay%20on%20pace%20even%20if%20UAW%20quickly%20wins%20higher%20wages%2C%20given%20many%20auto%20workers%20did%20not%20see%20major%20wage%20gains%20earlier%20in%20the%20pandemic%20given%20they%20were%20locked%20into%20contracts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-09-10%2Feven-a-brief-uaw-strike-seen-causing-billions-in-damage-to-us-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUAW%20President%20Shawn%20Fain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuaw.org%2Fuaw-auto-bargaining%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20demanded%3C%2Fa%3E%20retiree%20healthcare%20and%20traditional%20pension%20payment%20plans%2C%20which%20were%20taken%20away%20for%20new%20hires%20in%202007.%20To%20better%20protect%20union%20members%20from%20inflation%2C%20the%20union%20has%20pushed%20for%20a%20return%20to%20cost-of-living%20adjustments%2C%2032-hour%20workweeks%2C%20and%20an%20immediate%20raise%20of%2020%25%20followed%20by%20four%20additional%205%25%20raises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20has%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20companies'%20transition%20to%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20which%20have%20fewer%20moving%20parts%20and%20require%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famericafirstpolicy.com%2Flatest%2Fresearch-report-proposed-ev-mandate-would-eliminate-117000-auto-manufacturing-jobs%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAutomakers%2520like%2520Ford%2520and%2520Volkswagen%2Cquarters%2520of%2520auto%2520manufacturing%2520workers.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%25%20to%2040%25%20less%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20assemble%20than%20gasoline-powered%20cars%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20negotiate%20in%20Detroit%2024%2F7%2C%20just%20as%20we%20have%20been%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20weeks%20since%20we%20gave%20them%20our%20Members%20Demands%2C%26quot%3B%20Fain%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20receiving%20no%20response%20for%20over%20a%20month%2C%20when%20the%20CEOs%20are%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20serious%20offer%20we'll%20be%20there%2C%20day%20or%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20reported%20that%20these%20wage%20increases%20and%20other%20changes%20could%20amount%20to%20over%20%2480%20billion%20in%20additional%20expenses%20for%20each%20company%20over%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies%20that%20heavily%20rely%20on%20these%20automakers%2C%20such%20as%20auto-parts%20makers%2C%20which%20get%20as%20much%20as%20one-third%20of%20their%20revenue%20from%20these%20three%20companies%2C%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20see%20major%20drops%20in%20earnings%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20reported%20a%20UAW%20strike%20against%20any%20of%20the%20automakers%20could%20have%20a%20similar%20impact%20on%20the%20auto%20industry%20as%20the%20six-week%202019%20GM%20strike%2C%20which%20cost%20GM%20about%20%242.9%20billion%20and%20hurt%20auto-parts%20makers%20and%20steel%20producers.%20Steel%20production%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAW%20has%20rejected%20offers%20from%20the%20three%20companies%2C%20which%20included%20pay%20raises%20between%2014.5%25%20and%2016%25%20for%20most%20union%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20could%20seep%20into%20politics%20as%20campaigning%20picks%20up%20for%20the%202024%20presidential%20election.%20Key%20swing%20states%20such%20as%20Michigan%20and%20Wisconsin%20would%20likely%20take%20large%20economic%20hits%20from%20the%20strike%2C%20which%20could%20hurt%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20chances%20of%20winning%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECar%20prices%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FCUUR0000SETA01%230%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeen%20leveling%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20manufacturers%20have%20built%20up%20inventories%20since%20the%20big%20price%20spikes%20at%20the%20height%20of%20pandemic%20supply-chain%20woes.%20But%20a%20strike%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-strike-high-prices-low-inventory-car-deals-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20into%20those%20inventories%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20renewed%20price%20hikes%20and%20a%20new%20round%20of%20customer%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fbusiness%2Fautomakers-strike-negotiations-uaw%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20last%20week%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20expected%20the%20strike%20to%20be%20avoided%2C%20though%20he%20lacks%20the%20legal%20authority%20to%20order%20both%20sides%20to%20continue%20working.%20Deputy%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Wally%20Adeyemo%20confirmed%20to%20CNBC%20Monday%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20anticipated%20a%20deal%20between%20UAW%20and%20automakers%20after%20appointing%20top%20officials%20to%20help%20facilitate%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAW%2C%20which%20has%20historically%20supported%20Democrats%2C%20has%20not%20endorsed%20Biden's%20reelection%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20our%20strike%20can%20reaffirm%20to%20%5BBiden%5D%20of%20where%20the%20working-class%20people%20in%20this%20country%20stand%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20time%20for%20politicians%20in%20this%20country%20to%20pick%20a%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Fain%20said%20during%20CNBC's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Flast-call%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELast%20Call%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20with%20Brian%20Sullivan.%20%26quot%3BEither%20you%20stand%20for%20a%20billionaire%20class%20where%20everybody%20else%20gets%20left%20behind%2C%20or%20you%20stand%20for%20the%20working%20class%2C%20the%20working-class%20people%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauto-industry-uaw-strike-effects-inflation-michigan-recession-biden-election-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694471605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fb3e2da39a1b00190bd21f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauto-industry-uaw-strike-effects-inflation-michigan-recession-biden-election-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20UAW%20strike%20would%20a