that%20I'm%20potentially%20damaging%20the%20display%20with%20the%20pressure%20from%20my%20thumb%2C%20or%20that%20I%20might%20be%20scratching%20it%20with%20my%20thumbnail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20you%20could%20easily%20flick%20the%20phone%20open%20one-handed%20with%20your%20thumb%2C%20like%20the%20flip%20phones%20of%20yore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Unfolding%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%20with%20a%20single%20hand%20by%20thumb.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef3b146f301e00193dec05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnfolding%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%20with%20one%20hand%20is%20an%20awkward%20experience.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Z%20Flip%205%20unfolds%20to%20reveal%20a%20large%206.7-inch%20screen%2C%20but%20its%20width%20is%20akin%20to%20a%206.1-inch%20display.%20With%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20unfolded%20Z%20Flip%205%20doesn't%20really%20feel%20like%20a%206.7-inch%20phone%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20tall%206.1-inch%20phone%2C%20as%20apps%20and%20content%20can%20feel%20more%20cramped%20width-wise%20than%20a%20traditional%206.7-inch%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%E2%80%99s%20unfolded%20to%20reveal%20its%20display.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee38af8f917700193a2c57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%E2%80%99s%206.7-inch%20display%20is%20narrower%20than%20a%20traditional%20flat%20phone%E2%80%99s%20display%2C%20and%20the%20experience%20is%20closer%20to%20a%20long%206.1-inch%20screen.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cover%20screen%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Z%20Flip%205%20cover%20screen%20i