0cover%20display%2C%20called%20the%20Flex%20Window%2C%20is%20multitudes%20more%20useful%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20do%20everything%20the%20smaller%20cover%20displays%20could%20while%20seeing%20significantly%20more%20information%2C%20or%20at%20least%20see%20the%20information%20more%20clearly.%20You%20can%20also%20access%20basic%20settings%20like%20airplane%20mode%20or%20the%20flashlight%2C%20and%20even%20write%20a%20text%20with%20a%20full-size%20keyboard%20without%20needing%20to%20unfold%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222998%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%20in%20the%20folded%20position%20showing%20the%20cover%20display%20running%20the%20text%20message%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee3c00d1f80d00192f211c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUsing%20the%20cover%20screen%20to%20write%20a%20quick%20text%20message%20is%20convenient%2C%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20force%20you%20to%20unfold%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20little%20support%20for%20third-party%20apps%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20but%20some%20exist%2C%20like%20Google%20Maps%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20YouTube%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20The%20Z%20Flip%205's%20cover%20display%20would%20benefit%20from%20more%20third-party%20app%20support%2C%20but%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20more%20developers%20will%20make%20their%20apps%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20while%20many%20messaging%20apps%20aren't%20supported%20on%20the%20cover%20display%2C%20you%20can%20at%20least%20reply%20to%20messages%20on%20various%20apps%20like%20Instagram%20and%20Google%20Chat%20when%20you%20tap%20on%20the%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20Z%20Flip%205's%20larger%20cover%20display%20lets%20you%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20previous%20Z%20Flip%20phones%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20sig