gn%20makes%20for%20a%20convenient%20experience%20while%20recording%20videos%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20place%20the%20Z%20Flip%205%20on%20a%20surface%20in%20a%20half-folded%20laptop%20mode%2C%20which%20frees%20your%20hands%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20handy%20tripod.%20That's%20a%20legitimate%20perk%20for%20on-the-go%20content%20creators%2C%20or%20if%20you've%20ever%20wished%20you%20could%20record%20videos%20hands-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20actively%20looking%20to%20upgrade%20from%20an%20older%20Z%20Flip%20phone%2C%20and%20you%20can%20trade%20in%20your%20phone%20for%20the%20price%20of%20a%20new%20Z%20Flip%205%20from%20your%20carrier%2C%20it's%20a%20worthwhile%20upgrade%20thanks%20to%20its%20larger%2C%20revamped%20cover%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20considering%20to%20swap%20their%20flat%20phones%20for%20a%20foldable%20phone%2C%20just%20make%20sure%20to%20take%20some%20of%20the%20caveats%20into%20consideration%2C%20like%20the%20potential%20inconvenience%20with%20unfolding%20the%20phone%20when%20you%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20most%20essential%20tasks%2C%20despite%20the%20Z%20Flip%205's%20larger%20and%20slightly%20more%20useful%20cover%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20consider%20that%20the%20Z%20Flip%205's%20battery%20doesn't%20last%20as%20long%20as%20a%206.7-inch%20flat%20phone's%2C%20and%20you'll%20get%20better%20cameras%20on%20a%20similarly%20priced%20flat%20phone.%20Whether%20these%20are%20worthy%20compromises%20in%20exchange%20for%20novelty%2C%20easy%20hands-free%20content%20capture%2C%20or%20a%20compact%20package%20is%20up%20to%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-flip-5-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publis