0meeting%2C%20Modi%20described%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20strategic%20partners.%20Last%20Saturday%2C%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20were%20joined%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20in%20launching%20an%20ambitious%20plane%20for%20an%20economic%20corridor%20linking%20Indian%20ports%20through%20shipping%20and%20rail%20links%20to%20Europe%20via%20the%20Gulf%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20briefing%20following%20the%20talks%2C%20MEA%20secretary%20(CPV)%20Ausaf%20Sayeed%20said%20leaders%20were%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20early%20implementation%20of%20the%20West%20Coast%20refinery%20project%20for%20which%20funds%20worth%20%2450%20billion%20have%20been%20allotted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20set%20up%20a%20joint%20task%20force%20to%20help%20in%20identifying%20and%20channelising%20the%20USD%20100%20billion%20investments%20which%20was%20promised%20by%20the%20Saudi%20side%20half%20of%20which%20was%20for%20the%20refinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37110%2FJoint_Statement_during_the_State_Visit_of_HRH_the_Crown_Prince_and_Prime_Minister_of_the_Kingdom_of_Saudi_Arabia_to_India%5C%22%3EThe%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20after%20the%20talks%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20sides%20agreed%20to%20develop%20joint%20projects%20to%20transform%20oil%20into%20petrochemicals%20in%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20and%20providing%20the%20necessary%20support%2C%20requirements%20and%20enablers%20to%20accelerate%20the%20project%20of%20West%20Coast%20Refinery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20explore%20investment%20opportunities%20in%20the%20field%20of%20fertilisers%20and%20intermediate%2C%20transformative%20and%20specialised%20petrochemicals%20in%20both%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20eight%20pacts%20were%20inked%20for%20cooperation%20in%20a%20range%20of%20areas%20including%20investment%2C%20digitisation%2C%20and%20saltwater%20desalinisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra-based%20West%20Coast%20refinery%20project%2C%20initially%20unveiled%20in%202015%2C%20is%20a%20joint%20project%20between%20ARAMCO%2C%20ADNOC%2C%20and%20Indian%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20also%20agreed%20to%20establish%20a%20monitoring%20committee%20for%20tracking%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20refinery%20project%2C%20as%20per%20the%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20area%20of%20defence%20sector%2C%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20on%20continuing%20to%20consider%20possibilities%20of%20joint%20development%20and%20production%20of%20defence%20equipment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20announced%20that%20they%20agreed%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimportance%20of%20cooperation%20to%20promote%20ways%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20and%20safety%20of%20waterways%20and%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20in%20line%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20(UNCLOS)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20underlined%20the%20need%20to%20strengthen%20security%20cooperation%20in%20combating%20terrorism%20and%20its%20financing.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20sides%20emphasised%20that%20terrorism%2C%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20gravest%20threats%20to%20humanity.%20They%20agreed%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20justification%20for%20any%20act%20of%20terror%20for%20any%20reason%20whatsoever.%20They%20rejected%20any%20attempt%20to%20link%20terrorism%20to%20any%20particular%20race%2C%20religion%20or%20culture.%20Both%20sides%20called%20on%20all%20States%20to%20reject%20the%20use%20of%20terrorism%20against%20other%20countries%2C%20dismantle%20terrorism%20infrastructure%20where%20it%20exists%20and%20bring%20perpetrators%20of%20terrorism%20to%20justice%20swiftly%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprevent%20access%20to%20weapons%20including%20missiles%20and%20drones%20to%20commit%20terrorist%20acts%20against%20other%20countries%E2%80%9D.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20been%20targeted%20by%20frequent%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%20by%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20Iran-backed%20Houthis%20after%20the%20Saudi-led%20military%20coalition%20intervened%20to%20remove%20the%20Yemeni%20government%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20remarks%2C%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20recognised%20the%20substantial%20impact%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20residing%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20comprising%207%25%20of%20the%20Saudi%20population.%20He%20reiterated%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20considers%20them%20an%20integral%20component%20of%20the%20nation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20consider%20them%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20We%20watch%20and%20take%20care%20of%20them%20like%20we%20take%20care%20of%20our%20own%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694454250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11230929%2FF5u9Jfqa8AAj2Mz.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-saudi-arabia-agree-to-accelerate-50-billion-west-coast-refinery-project%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20a%20discussion%20with%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20Bin%20Salman%20Bin%20Abdulaziz%20Al-Saud%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20described%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20strategic%20partners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-saudi-arabia-agree-to-accelerate-50-billion-west-coast-refinery-project%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canadian%20Armed%20Forces'%20Plane%2