ing%20them%20how%20to%20cultivate%20millets%2C%20such%20as%20ragi%2C%20jowar%2C%20proso%20millet%2C%20and%20pearl%20millet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20vegetables%2C%20including%20exotic%20ones%20like%20zucchini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20country%2C%20Sharmila%E2%80%99s%20son%20Shubham%20was%20at%20home%20after%20completing%20his%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20political%20science%20at%20Ashoka%20University.%20A%20conversation%20about%20millets%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20healthy%20food%20choices%20sparked%20the%20idea%20for%20their%20startup%2C%20%E2%80%98Gud%20Mom%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20time%20at%20the%20university%2C%20I%20saw%20most%20of%20my%20friends%20consuming%20junk%20food.%20We%20also%20saw%20many%20youngsters%20affected%20by%20lifestyle%20diseases.%20To%20help%20combat%20this%20and%20also%20provide%20a%20good%20market%20for%20farmers%2C%20we%20launched%20a%20startup%20based%20on%20a%20farm-to-fork%20model%20to%20sell%20millet%20grains%20and%20healthy%20millet-based%20snacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shubham%20Oswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Gud%20Mom%E2%80%99%20sells%20millet%20noodles%2C%20pasta%2C%20cookies%2C%20crackers%2C%20herb%20sticks%20and%20more%20through%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgudmom.com%2Fcollections%2Fall%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20Amazon%2C%20and%20via%20other%20retailers.%20Most%20of%20the%20grains%20and%20ready-to-eat%20items%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%2048%20and%20Rs%20150.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrDtZGVrPeU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrDtZGVrPeU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdi