0the%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20two%20cows%20but%20later%20I%20bought%20four%20more%20cows%20to%20get%20more%20cow%20dung.%20I%20also%20source%20at%20least%2030%20truckloads%20of%20cow%20dung%20from%20farmers%20to%20boost%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20set%20up%2010%20vermicompost%20beds%20each%20of%2010%C3%973%20feet%20in%20size.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20she%20has%20also%20set%20up%20a%2085%C3%9735%20feet%20vermicompost%20bed%20on%201.5%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eland%20of%20her%20family.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20able%20to%20produce%20up%20to%2035%20tonnes%20of%20vermicompost%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kanika%20sells%20the%20products%20to%20Assam's%20agriculture%20department%20and%20to%20at%20least%2025%20nurseries%20across%20Meghalaya%2C%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%2C%20and%20Nagaland.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1693896930-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329063%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKanika%20sells%20her%20products%20to%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20department%20and%20to%20at%20least%2025%20nurseries%20across%20Meghalaya%2C